======
Draco2
======

This is Draco2, a dynamic web application framework in Python.

Prerequisites
-------------

Draco2 depends on the following packages. They need to be installed before you can
install Draco2.

 * Python_: Our favourite scripting language. Version 2.4 or later is required.
 * psycopg2_: A DB-API compatible interface to PostgreSQL_. Version 2.0.5 is
   tested, later versions should work.
 * lxml_: A *Pythonic* interface to XML for Python. Version 1.1.2 is tested,
   later version should work.
 * gdmodule_: A Python interface to the gd "graphic-draw" library.

Installation instructions
-------------------------

Draco2 uses distutils so installation is easy::

  $ python setup.py build
  $ python setup.py install

Geert Jansen
April 2007

